Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.23,0:00:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.54,0:00:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.65,0:00:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.52,0:00:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.56,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.54,0:00:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.38,0:00:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.31,0:00:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.69,0:01:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.52,0:01:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,八神,多保重哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.95,0:01:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.62,0:01:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀!有小偷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.09,0:01:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!偷窺狂!有偷窺狂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.80,0:01:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.60,0:01:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五…五代先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.38,0:01:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.55,0:01:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.55,0:02:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.05,0:02:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,我平安回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的鞋子呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.46,0:02:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來老師真的嚇壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師,我們又能見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.25,0:02:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#65 八神慘叫!\N四谷的危險個人授課!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.56,0:02:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.76,0:02:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.13,0:02:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽,營養午餐費,營養午餐費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你實在有夠笨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事要昨天提早跟我講…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.67,0:02:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.64,0:02:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心車子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.84,0:02:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.62,0:03:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.39,0:03:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣可能又會變熱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.90,0:03:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然在八神家出了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.33,0:03:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?\N妳叫五代老師從窗戶逃走?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家教的事,我沒有跟我爸媽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.94,0:03:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊\N難得兩個人可以獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.61,0:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳爸媽沒有回來\N妳打算做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦,悅子\N妳想太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.25,0:03:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼?什麼事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的不懂嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.63,0:03:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.76,0:03:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後妳打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師\N不會再當妳的家教了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.57,0:04:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這雙球鞋還給他之後\N一切就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天還是不要還吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.97,0:04:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竹葉沙沙作響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.61,0:04:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒲島救了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.42,0:04:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.19,0:04:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,妳還記得我啊\N實在太感動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.92,0:05:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔真的很''黑皮''
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這要給五代的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這憂愁的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.84,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳有什麼煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把電話號碼告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,這雙舊的請幫我拿去丟掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩還真傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.65,0:05:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N不過,其實她心地很善良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.45,0:06:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個年紀的女孩\N專情得會令人害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.56,0:06:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也曾經有過這種時期啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.00,0:06:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別看我這樣\N其實我很容易著迷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.11,0:06:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能明白八神的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.41,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,因為這次的事\N終於能跟她斷絕關係了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.15,0:06:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.59,0:06:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,怎麼這麼晚才回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐在這裡幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.86,0:06:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在等你回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.86,0:06:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有一位楚楚動人\N而且憂愁的美少女來找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.80,0:06:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,託我把這包東西交給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.14,0:06:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有留話給我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.92,0:07:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只說''很抱歉給你添麻煩了''
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會這麼乾脆,感覺怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是吃的東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,拿去吃,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.59,0:07:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喝的真快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.29,0:07:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正一定跟管理員有關\N是不是有什麼好事發生啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近很有女人緣耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連高中女生都迷你迷得要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個不算啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.44,0:07:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我已經跟她斷絕關係了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.84,0:08:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上特別熱鬧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.24,0:08:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的兩三天都平安無事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳今天來有什麼事嗎?八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.99,0:08:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是上家教的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家教?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次明明就已經結束…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.84,0:09:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安,四谷老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.61,0:09:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.71,0:09:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷老師,你好帥喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,跟我來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.63,0:09:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先別問,來就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.66,0:09:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.50,0:09:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噓,小聲點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.31,0:09:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,妳知道四谷\N是個怎麼樣的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.11,0:09:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想這樣說我的房客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正不可以就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.92,0:09:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是那種會在街上放毒氣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,職業不明,年紀不詳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇人,怪人,寄生蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.49,0:10:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這實在太驚人了\N連叔叔我都嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小莉加也嚇到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.40,0:10:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進,我的房間很簡陋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.27,0:10:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.81,0:10:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,四谷老師的房間好漂亮喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可以放著不管嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能眼睜睜的看著\N我以前教過的學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.39,0:10:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落入變態的魔掌之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能讓公寓裡發生醜聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逼不得已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.78,0:10:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想玩什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.22,0:10:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛,玩老師喜歡玩的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.99,0:11:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡玩的啊,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說橋牌或是西洋棋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.40,0:11:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,果然還是偷窺最好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.24,0:11:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到一點牆壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,我問妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.48,0:11:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以握妳的手嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪,紙拉門裡面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要握人家的手喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.59,0:11:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我可以輕輕的摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.36,0:11:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道他知道我們在這裡\N所以才故意那麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師,我來泡咖啡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.86,0:11:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,我來拿咖啡杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.40,0:11:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你在幹什…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.78,0:12:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼以後要在\N五代老師的房間上課啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.78,0:12:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,又可以跟老師在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.72,0:12:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N雖然不能兩人單獨在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.06,0:12:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,能在同一個房間\N渡過同樣的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就很滿足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.63,0:12:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,妳還真不害臊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個寡婦會擺出一張臭臉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.14,0:12:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法\N因為她還會在旁邊偷看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.54,0:13:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷看什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.45,0:13:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?偷看?\N誰在偷看什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是看妳的書吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.31,0:13:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉在地上的東西\N會吃壞肚子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.75,0:13:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳啊,八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出來散步嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師回來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.36,0:14:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說,跟四谷老師單獨在一起\N我還真的有點怕怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也害妳替我擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.84,0:14:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,有五代老師陪在身邊\N我就能安心唸書了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好用功加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.62,0:14:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我會努力的\N功課方面也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.52,0:14:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.91,0:14:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛來嘛,喝一杯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.88,0:14:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,唸書…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.72,0:14:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唸書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.26,0:15:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼?人家在唸書耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.16,0:15:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係,我們來打氣慰問啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.20,0:15:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們第一次\N看到四谷在工作耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.27,0:15:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是八神在唸書耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.37,0:15:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不在意\N請不用管那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.58,0:15:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.18,0:15:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的房間有人會來偷窺\N沒有辦法專心唸書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.29,0:15:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就如上次決定的\N以後在這個房間唸書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有做這種決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是要在我的房間唸嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你不能偷窺喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.17,0:15:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,唸書唸書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.79,0:16:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉\N為了八神變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,我是無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這樣下去,你會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.70,0:16:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種環境\N我不相信八神能專心唸書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.91,0:16:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要家教那天不回來就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.65,0:16:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼?茶會涼掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,馬上來馬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.39,0:16:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.14,0:16:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送她去車站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.51,0:17:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改天再一起唸書喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.55,0:17:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.95,0:17:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.49,0:17:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我走了,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.12,0:17:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師,快走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.06,0:17:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過說真的,這還真累人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕真好,沒有羞恥心\N也不在乎別人的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.90,0:17:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,看五代被她耍得團團轉\N搞不好五代他自己也很高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.57,0:17:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說要送她回去\N馬上就被拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.41,0:17:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.56,0:17:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.20,0:17:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,妳來參加研修會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.37,0:17:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,今天比較早結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.77,0:18:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後,五代過得好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.37,0:18:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,很好,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.49,0:18:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼早就開始了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八…八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.00,0:18:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,這雙鞋子是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.54,0:18:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是今天明明不是家教的日子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.18,0:18:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是因為四谷工作的關係\N而改成今天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.40,0:19:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.13,0:19:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔\N今天怎麼這麼晚還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他去哪裡鬼混了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒什麼重要的事\N居然還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.10,0:19:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他也沒有錢鬼混
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.47,0:19:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是故意\N避開這個時間不回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.21,0:19:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我叫錢德勒.四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.35,0:19:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們都叫我飛利浦.四谷.馬龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.90,0:20:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,打擾妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,請不用介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,真的很頭痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.71,0:20:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管再怎麼專情\N就算是我也覺得實在太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.31,0:20:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,要不要吃餅乾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.72,0:20:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是人家送的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.59,0:20:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.19,0:20:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.16,0:20:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在的話,我要進去囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.40,0:20:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.97,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茶點還沒好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,不好意思,馬上拿過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.34,0:20:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-拜託妳了\N-那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼,妳有客人啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,鄰居的太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.49,0:21:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天的晚餐,我想吃炸蝦蓋飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.59,0:21:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧?五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.03,0:21:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼?五代不在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後天要吃豬排蓋飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.93,0:21:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要關門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大後天要吃雞肉蓋飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.64,0:21:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大大後天要吃鰻魚蓋飯\N外加魚肝湯,還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.05,0:21:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.22,0:21:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.42,0:21:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是,你絕對不能告訴八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.16,0:21:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然不會說\N因為這關係到我的晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.56,0:21:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你要遵守約定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.63,0:21:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.77,0:21:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.18,0:21:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.51,0:22:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,晚餐泡湯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事?管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.69,0:22:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在問妳這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.73,0:22:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.53,0:22:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳騙我\N原來妳把他藏起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.70,0:22:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,八神…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.57,0:22:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師,你不要講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.57,0:22:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳就那麼想拆散\N我跟五代老師嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.62,0:22:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?怎麼這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.12,0:22:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個寡婦來向妳告狀嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.55,0:22:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說話謹慎一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.49,0:22:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐是擔心妳\N所以才好心告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.73,0:22:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先別管這個,這是前幾天\N模擬考試的成績單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.47,0:22:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,妳拿去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.87,0:22:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳退步了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.00,0:23:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳現在請的家教老師\N好像一點用處都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.96,0:23:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了她,絕對饒不了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.09,0:23:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然來跟老師打小報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.86,0:23:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然妳要那麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.57,0:23:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會抗戰到底!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.72,0:23:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要是喜歡五代老師就明說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.46,0:23:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們已經對上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.16,0:23:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是女高中生,膽子真大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.50,0:23:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻,下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.03,0:23:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「八神的挑戰!\N我才不會輸給寡婦」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.63,0:24:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和五代老師接吻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.95,0:24:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.43,0:24:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.15,0:24:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.42,0:24:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.82,0:25:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.00,0:25:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.97,0:25:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.37,0:25:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.81,0:25:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢…濡濕而發光
